description:
Third-party libraries and header files that are prerequisites for building the Aerospike C client.
This package is only designed to help build the Aerospike C client library.

Separate deployment packages (aerospike-client-c, aerospike-client-c-libuv and 
aerospike-client-c-libevent) are used to build customer applications with Aerospike.

Libraries (64 bit):

getopt 1.0.2
libevent 2.1.8
libuv 1.15.0
lua 5.1.5
openssl 1.0.2
pthreads 2.10.0
zlib 1.2.8.8
summary: Third-party libraries and header files that are prerequisites for building the Aerospike C client.
title: Aerospike C Client Build Dependencies
